msgid "FlowProxy"
msgstr "代理分流"

msgid "flowproxy"
msgstr "代理分流"

msgid "traffic diversion based on nftables rules. the service will automatically start/stop when you click \"save & apply\"."
msgstr "基于 nftables 规则的流量分流。点击“保存并应用”后，服务将自动启动/停止。"

msgid "define nftables rules. choose match type and provide value (IP, MAC, or @set)."
msgstr "定义 nftables 规则。选择匹配类型并提供匹配值（IP、MAC 或 @名单引用）。"

msgid "define nftables rules. choose match type and provide value. rules are separated into TCP and UDP lists."
msgstr "定义 nftables 规则。选择匹配类型并提供匹配值。规则已拆分为 TCP 和 UDP 独立列表。"

msgid "manage nftables set collections. use the global \"save & apply\" button at the bottom to take effect."
msgstr "管理 nftables set 集合。使用底部的全局“保存并应用”按钮以生效。"

msgid "manage nftables set collections. you can use predefined lists or add custom ones at the bottom."
msgstr "管理 nftables set 集合。您可以使用预设名单或在底部添加自定义名单。"

msgid "configure and view service runtime logs."
msgstr "配置并查看服务运行日志。"

msgid "view the generated configuration and live kernel state."
msgstr "查看生成的配置及内核实时运行状态。"

